noop through my employer’s things. \r\n\r\nINSPECTOR:  May we search your house? This is routine. We’re asking everyone that was at the mansion that night. Otherwise, we can get a warrant. \r\n\r\nCLAIRE:  You don’t need to threaten me. I’ve nothing to hide.\r\n\r\nINSPECTOR:  Thank you, Claire. You have been very helpful.',
